headline: DLC Acquires Two Walmart Supercenter-Anchored Shopping Centers in Columbus, Ohio
summary: ELMSFORD, NEW YORK / ACCESSWIRE / December 23, 2024 / DLC, one of the nation's leading owners and operators of open-air shopping centers, has announced the acquisition of two premier Walmart Supercenter-anchored shopping centers in Columbus, Ohio ...
